Benchmarks for Central Processor
--------------------------------

On Cray XT3 at WASP (marron):
----------------------------
To compile:
  cd src
  make clean all

To run:
  cd ../scripts
  ./runParallelIO -l -f <filesize in MB> -b <bufsize in MB> -p <lustre_path> -o <output_file> <number nodes list>
  <number nodes list> example: 1 2 4 8 16 32 64

On CSIRO IBM PC Blades (burnet):
-------------------------
Before compilation, load the following modules:
  module load intel-cc mpich2

To compile:
  cd src
  make clean all

To run:
  cd ../scripts
  ./runParallelIO -f <filesize in MB> -b <bufsize in MB> -p <cs data path> -o <output_file> <number of nodes>


